《'''路德探長'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Luther'''''}}）是一部[[英國|英國]]罪案類電視劇，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00sbjbv|title=Luther|work=BBC|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150603162301/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00sbjbv|dead-url=no}}</ref>由尼爾‧克羅斯（Neil Cross）創作，[[伊德瑞斯‧艾爾巴|伊德瑞斯‧艾爾巴]]飾演男主角偵緝總督察約翰‧-{zh-tw:路瑟;zh-cn:路德;zh-hk:路德;}-（John Luther）。第一季六集於2010年5月4日至6月8日在[[BBC_One|BBC One]]播出，第二季四集於2011年6月至7月播出，第三季四集於2013年7月播出，第四季二集於2015年12月播出，第五季四集於2019年1月播出。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2012/luther-3-release.html | title = Sienna Guillory joins Idris Elba in the third series of Luther | publisher = BBC.co.uk | accessdate = 8 March 2015 | archive-date = 2015-09-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925071855/http://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2012/luther-3-release.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

伊德瑞斯‧艾爾巴憑藉在此劇中的表演獲得了[[第68屆金球獎|第68屆]]、[[第69屆金球獎|第69屆]]以及[[第71屆金球獎|第71屆]]三屆[[金球獎|金球獎]]的「迷你劇或電視電影類最佳男主角」的提名，並在第69屆獲得了這項大獎。<ref>{{cite news |title=Golden Globes: Idris Elba wins for actor in a TV miniseries |url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2012/01/golden-globes-idris-elba-best-actor-in-a-mini-series-or-tv-movie.html |last=Saad |first=Nardine |work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] |agency=Showtracker (blog) |accessdate=16 January 2012 |date=16 January 2012 |archive-date=2014-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221134919/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/showtracker/2012/01/golden-globes-idris-elba-best-actor-in-a-mini-series-or-tv-movie.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=/film/26322|title=Luther 3 Nomination(s) 1 Win(s)|work=HFPA|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018091615/http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=%2Ffilm%2F26322|dead-url=no}}</ref>劇集還獲得了8項[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]提名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/luther|title=Luther|work=Primetime Emmy Awards|accessdate=2015-04-30|archive-date=2015-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416234921/http://www.emmys.com/shows/luther|dead-url=no}}</ref>

編劇尼爾‧克羅斯曾表示《路德探長》一劇不會繼續製作第四季，但有計畫推齣電影版本。<ref>{{cite web |author=Caroline Westbrook |url=http://metro.co.uk/2013/08/24/luther-creator-neil-cross-rules-out-fourth-series-of-bbc-one-show-3936421/ |title=Luther creator Neil Cross rules out fourth series of BBC One show | Metro News |publisher=Metro.co.uk |date=2013-08-24 |accessdate=2014-01-10 |archive-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103111231/http://metro.co.uk/2013/08/24/luther-creator-neil-cross-rules-out-fourth-series-of-bbc-one-show-3936421/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>但2014年11月，報導稱《路德》將繼續製作第四季，並將於2015年播出。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30128086 | title = Luther making his return to BBC One | publisher = BBC.co.uk | accessdate = 8 March 2015 | archive-date = 2015-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150221125448/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-30128086 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Team TVLine |url=http://tvline.com/2014/11/19/luther-season-4-bbc-america-idris-elba-2015-return/ |title='BBC America Slates Luther Season 4 |date=2014-11-19 |accessdate=2014-11-19 |archive-date=2014-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141121224817/http://tvline.com/2014/11/19/luther-season-4-bbc-america-idris-elba-2015-return/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

